### Agent Write Rules

The nightly OpenClaw agent may:
- Move inbox notes to `10_Projects/` or `20_Areas/`
- Update frontmatter `status` field
- Create/update `_Daily/<date>.md` files
- Create `_System/agent-log/<date>-nightly.md`
- Update the `AGENT:RECENT_CONTEXT` section of this file

The nightly agent must NOT:
- Modify transcript text or AI summaries in any note
- Create new project folders
- Write to `20_Areas/Life/` content (routing only)
- Write to `_System/Templates/` or `40_Archive/` or `30_Resources/`

Claude Code session assistant may:
- Read all vault content
- Write to `10_Projects/<domain>/<client>/` with user confirmation
- Create project index files
- Append to resource notes

